<br>
If one wanted to optimize mana regen (at 55th just for giggles), what would be the best items to obtain to do it?  Skills as well I suppose.  Let's prioritize easier things over harder things as well.<br>
<br>
For instance, I would say getting the epic is the best step.  Familiar spell would be good also.  What else?  Let's be exhaustive here. <p>Kazzap Allahandra 58 Wizard<BR>
Iskendar Woundtempest 53 Warrior<BR><BR>
Praise the good, hold your tongue when you can, bitch when it needs bitching.
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ualeolin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aleolin</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/31/01 11:02:06 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.oobalance.com/images/sig.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Optimizing Mana Regen</span><hr size=1> Buy a horse and get a manarobe.<br>
<br>
On horse you regen mana standing still, while you click the robe. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=23432>My Profile!</a>
<b> Aleolin Darkmoon ~ 57th Flame-Broiled Burner of Order of Balance </b>
<img src="http://www.oobalance.com/images/screenshots/129710686743Sig.jpg">
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ukazzap.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kazzap</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/31/01 11:03:57 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://kazzap.homestead.com/files/wizorb.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Optimizing Mana Regen</span><hr size=1> I guess you can put 3 points into mental clarity as well.<br>
<br>
What are the different FT items and med items available now? <p>Kazzap Allahandra 58 Wizard<BR>
Iskendar Woundtempest 53 Warrior<BR><BR>
Praise the good, hold your tongue when you can, bitch when it needs bitching.
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugaelron.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gaelron</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/1/02 2:40:33 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Mana Robe</span><hr size=1> Mana Robe is way too slow imho.. Get a manastone and gate back to old world.. much faster <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uyaxa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yaxa</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.remagination.net/yaxa/ynew.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/1/02 2:43:01 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.remagination.net/yaxa/yaxportrait.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Mana Robe</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Get a manastone and gate back to old world.. much faster<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
You forget that Manastones aren't readily available on all servers. On The Nameless there are only three total, and on the newer servers they don't even exist <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><CENTER> <BR><A HREF="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=65975"><IMG SRC="http://www.remagination.net/yaxa/yaxsig12.jpg" ALT="Yaxa Brightmoon" WIDTH="450" HEIGHT="80" BORDER="0"></A></CENTER></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/urombusmindspire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rombus Mindspire</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>Forum Sorcerer</font></td></tr></table><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>NOT Rhombus!</font></td></tr></table></span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/1/02 4:57:55 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.tritonguild.com/rombus/sidepic.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Mana Robe</span><hr size=1> It's actually faster to sit on your horse and click your manarobe than it is to zone and gate back.  In some zones you don't have the luxury of gating back as you always can't easily get back to the spot you're fighting at and it's not always safe to bind.<br>
<br>
Get the following: Horse, FT Item, Mental Clarity 3 (obviously optional), Mana Robe, 54 / 60 Familiar, and of course the obvious mind buffs if you can pull it.<br>
