<br>
Two catches:<br>
Only works in the old world.  But you can always gate to an old world spot and gate back to your hunting area.<br>
<br>
This is assuming you play on a server that has manastones.  Before the pre-specter nerf. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/usilverbladetheenchanter.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Silverblade the Enchanter</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/1/02 10:52:39 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.silverblades-suitcase.com/artofadreamer/3d/excaliburthumb1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: by far the best is mana regen...</span><hr size=1> Easy:<br>
get a lvl 56+ mage in your group.<br>
<br>
he can pop out mod rods mk2, Aka Rod of Mystic Transvergance.<br>
3 charges, 300 hp=220 mana per charge.<br>
<br>
Used right you can keep whole group FM...<br>
<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
